data.text:
Ms. Velasco completed a Summer internship with Stonelake in 2022.

Ms. Velasco received her B.B.A. in Finance with a certificate in Real Estate from the McCombs School of Business at the University of Texas at Austin. While attending UT, Ms. Velasco served as an analyst supporting the underwriting process for public and private investments on the McCombs Real Estate Investment Fund.
